    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// Spring Security 的过滤器链是责任链的典型应用</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nd">@Component</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">AuthFilter</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">extends</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">OncePerRequestFilter</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nd">@Override</span><span class="w">
